er to faith. See John </div><div class="t m7cd x92 h2d y12ae ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3:16; 1 John 5:11, 12. In the great day of final reward He will </div><div class="t mb49 x92 h2d y1c36 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">give the believers eternal life absolutely forevermore, and make </div><div class="t m58a x15 h2d y1eb4 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their frail bodies immortal. To the other class who have been </div><div class="t m3e5 x15 h2d ybbf ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">contentious and disobedient He will render the fruitage of their </div><div class="t m60c x15 h2d y1199 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">doings. They have refused to obey the truth, but have followed </div><div class="t m5af x92 h2d y1f4d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unrighteousness. To them belongs indignation and wrath, tribu- </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
